metadata.name: Your Sharkwitch
metadata.description:
This is Your Sharkwitch, the first piece of "GARRID2U" collection focused in character design and concept art without commitment.

The character has no name, no story, build yours!

Owning this piece gives you the right to use this character and the elements of the art for everything you want. No Rules, basically the character become yours.

The owner can request the full resolution final image .
